   THE NEW STAKES

   Founded in 2009, ADventori is a Creative Advertising Technology which
   personalizes, measures and optimizes digital advertising.

   Advertisers rely on our technical expertise and experience to run
   online data-driven campaigns: from messaging, data integration, to
   trafficking in all advertising formats. Beyond expected media
   optimisation and creative support, ADventori streamlines the technical
   execution of campaigns, creating productivity gains and an optimal
   business organization to manage a complex ecosystem.

   Our references: Renault, SFR, OUI.sncf, Fressnapf, GMF, Nissan,
   foodora, Mini, Decathlon, Samsung, Système U.

